snippet.title: Surviving the Aftermath - Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
The end of the world is upon us! Surviving the Aftermath will leave early access and launch November 16 on PC, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch.

For more details, read our blog post: https://pdxint.at/3nvPrpf

Follow us on social media to stay up-to-date with the latest news!
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/SurvivingPDX/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/Surviving_PDX
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/surviving_pdx/
PDX Discord - https://discord.gg/pdx

Paradox on YouTube:
---------------------------------
ParadoxInteractive - http://youtube.com/ParadoxInteractive
Trailers, Feature Breakdowns, Dev Diaries, and more.

ParadoxExtra - http://youtube.com/ParadoxExtra
Gameplay of our video games, convention coverage, and other fun things from Paradox!

Paradox Grand Strategy - http://youtube.com/ParadoxGrandStrategy
Gameplay of our Grand Strategy Games. CK2, EU4, HOI4, Stellaris, and Imperator.
